nodes.text: Irasal ke Voltin was a male Human Adumari who had a feud with Garatty ke Kith, another Adumari. Irasal ke Voltin planned on ambushing ke Kith as the latter made his way home, and while waiting for ke Kith in his apartment, ke Voltin bumped into Rogue Squadron pilots Wedge Antilles and Wes Janson, who were waiting for New Republic spy Iella Wessiri.
ke Voltin attacked and dueled ke Kith when he arrived home. ke Voltin won the duel and Janson believed ke Kith to be dead.
